# Code Review Checklist

Apply on every change. See `.opencode/agents/code-review.md` for the full checklist.

Architecture · Naming · Type safety · Performance · Accessibility · Security · Tests · Docs · Edge cases.

Reject:
- New `any` without migration plan.
- Snapshot tests as substitute for assertions.
- Bundle weight increases > 10% without justification.
- Coverage drop below gate.